[ Water lapping ]

00:21:47.407 --> 00:21:49.210 position:41% line:89% align:start
[ Growling softly ]

00:21:49.243 --> 00:21:52.747 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Rumbling ]

00:21:52.780 --> 00:21:54.715 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:21:54.749 --> 00:21:56.250 position:13% line:89% align:start
What was that?

00:21:56.284 --> 00:21:58.451 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Birds cawing ]

